---
title: Crispy Teriyaki Salmon with Green Beans and Jasmine Rice
description: So simple yet so many delectable flavours in this easy dish. Adding onion and ginger to the toasted rice brings out flavour for an easy side. Pair this with crispy-skinned sweet salmon and you're set for dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-teriyaki-salmon-82701dba.jpg
